msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Idan kuna a waje da Amurka, muna ba da shawarar NOWPayments (kudade mafi "
"ƙanƙanta, kai tsaye zuwa wallet ɗinku). Idan kuna a Amurka, Stripe Crypto ma"
" yana da zaɓi. Kuna iya kunna ayyuka da yawa kuma ku bari baƙinku su zaɓa!"

